Replaced direct `prisma.systemSetting.findMany` queries with `getSystemSettings` in multiple API and Admin routes to leverage Next.js caching and reduce database load. Also fixed strict type errors during the testing process.
---
 app/(public)/invoices/[id]/page.tsx    |  2 +-
 app/admin/system/seo/page.tsx          |  9 +++++----
 app/admin/system/settings/page.tsx     |  9 +++++----
 app/api/system/contact/route.ts        | 10 +++++-----
 app/api/system/email/route.ts          | 10 +++++-----
 app/api/system/seo/route.ts            | 10 +++++-----
 app/llms.txt/route.ts                  | 25 +++++++++++--------------
 lib/server/__tests__/marketing.test.ts |  2 +-
 8 files changed, 38 insertions(+), 39 deletions(-)

